<section>
    <h2>My Poems</h2>
    <div class="poem">
        <h3>Your Eyes</h3>
        <p>
            (Featured in "Sunset Hues")<br>
            Your eyes, a deep and endless sea,<br>
            Where stars reflect and set me free.<br>
            In their gaze, I find my peace,<br>
            A tranquil world, where sorrows cease.
        </p>
    </div>
